result.title: Coach required
result.content:
Hi, I need someone who can give me a properly charted schedule, with links of tutorials, and also teaching (clearning doubts and strengthening the concept) me DS/Algo. Also, giving me problems to solve, which involve nice tricks, from their experience. I can pay $15 an hour of teaching via Skype.

Your rating should be > 2200 for atleast 3 rounds. (Grandmaster for atleast 3 rounds) Also fluency in English is required.

Please comment if anyone is interested.

Thanks.
